Ruben Quirino em A Fortuna do Milionario

description: The easily accessible and beautifully illustrated World of WarCraft: The Ultimate Visual Guide presents the people, places, and events which make this blockbuster game so undeniably compelling. Packed full of up to date information for both established fans and newcomers to the world of Azeroth, this volume features exclusive, never-before-seen art and showcases gorgeous official artwork from the World of WarCraft universe. A highly entertaining overview of the characters, lore, locations, and events of World of WarCraft, including every expansion.
name: HC
